Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.matching.algorithms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MatchingAlgorithm<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>
    Interface for all matching algorithms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DuplicateBasedMatchingAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    Implementation of duplicate-based matching: the values of the given duplicates are compared and vote for correspondences.
    EnsembleMatchingAlgorithm<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>
    Ensemble that combines the results of multiple matchers.
    GreedyOneToOneMatchingAlgorithm<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>
    Takes a set of correspondences as input and returns a set of correspondences in which every element can only part of one correspondence.
    InstanceBasedSchemaMatchingAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    Implementation of instance-based schema matching: the schemas are matched by comparing the values of the schema elements.
    MaximumBipartiteMatchingAlgorithm<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>  
    RuleBasedDuplicateDetectionAlgorithm<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>
    Implementation of rule-based identity resolution for the special case of a single data set (=duplicate detection)
    RuleBasedMatchingAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable,CorrespondenceType extends Matchable>
    Implementation of rule-based matching.
    RuleLearner<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    Class that controls the learning of matching rules
    SimpleDuplicateDetectionAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    Implementation of instance-based schema matching: the schemas are matched by comparing the values of the schema elements.
    SimpleIdentityResolutionAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    Implementation of instance-based schema matching: the schemas are matched by comparing the values of the schema elements.
    SymmetricInstanceBasedSchemaMatchingAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
    A variant of the InstanceBasedSchemaMatchingAlgorithm that uses only a single input dataset.
    TransitiveCorrespondencesCreator<TypeA extends Matchable,TypeB extends Matchable>
    Takes a set of correspondences as input and creates all correspondences that can be inferred by transitivity
    VectorSpaceIdentityResolutionAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>  
    VectorSpaceInstanceBasedSchemaMatchingAlgorithm<RecordType extends Matchable,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
